data.description: This home has been reduced for a quick sale. The seller is relocating and is very MOTIVATED to sell. Bring all offers for this Beautiful home that is well-maintained. It is a 4-sided brick home, nestled on a safe & quiet, street in the Wind Lake Estates neighborhood. This Gorgeous home has everything you want & need. The rooms are all spacious and the bedrooms have large closet spaces. Also, there's a Huge "FULL FINISHED" Basement with an in-law design which includes a large bedroom, a Full Bathroom, a large open area for entertaining plus a separate room used for a gym. In addition, there's a workroom and storage area.   The Roof is in great condition, plus the full-size "POOL" is covered and just needs cleaning. There are many more features that you just have to see!
